OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry for most places today with
OL,6,Fvariable amounts of cloud and sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Showery outbreaks of rain in
OL,8,Fplaces, mainly in the north. Turning
OL,9,Fcold in the north
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud and patchy rain moving
OL,12,Fsouth tonight. but many places staying
OL,13,Fdry. Blustery showers in Scotland,
OL,14,Fturning wintry in the Northern Isles.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FMost places dry with patchy
OL,17,Fcloud and sunny spells. A few showers
OL,18,Fbreaking out across Northern Ireland,
OL,19,FWales and southwest England.
OL,20,FTemperatures below average for the
OL,21,Ftime of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
